                  Java 21 • Spring Boot • PostgreSQL • TypeScript
                </div>
                <p class="card__description">
                  Built originally as a solo project for Code Ninjas, then
                  deployed across multiple locations supporting 20+ active
                  student accounts. The platform uses isolated multi-tenant data,
                  JWT auth, role hierarchy, a responsive TypeScript SPA, and an
                  immutable ledger as the source of truth for balances; the next
                  step is broader dojo availability with Code Ninjas engineers.
                </p>
                <div class="card__tags">
