                <p class="card__description">
                  A handmade jewelry business needed a polished custom-order flow
                  without the weight of a full storefront. I built an Astro site
                  with a WebP-optimized gallery, reusable request modal,
                  Resend-powered emails, and a Shopify-free path for bespoke
                  orders.
                </p>
                <div class="card__tags">
                  <span class="tag">AI-Assisted</span>
